<varlistentry id="options.NoPPosition">
	<term>NoPPosition</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Species that afterstep should ignore the  PPosition  field  when
		placing  new windows, in other words, windows can't choose where
		to place  themselves.   Adherence  to  the  PPosition  field  is
		required for some applications.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
